== RE: Deletion of "Community:5 Пятёрочка Russian" ==

Hello! I'm writing this here to notify you that the page you created- "[[Community:5 Пятёрочка Russian]]"- was deleted for violation of our Conflict of Interest policies, as you are clearly credited as a primary contributor to the world- and thus disallowed from creating a page on said world (or making any non-minor edits, such as spelling or grammatical errors). The world ''*is*'' notable enough to be included on the Wiki, but notability ''*cannot*'' be defined by anyone responsible for the world itself. It must come from the community's own interest and the available information ''*about*'' the world online.

If you'd like to see a page be created for the world, try reaching out to a maintainer or posting a request on our Discord server! We ''*admittedly*'' don't quite yet have the most proper procedure for submitting page requests, but it's something we're working on making easier and more accessible to the public internet over time. I also VERY MUCH recommend publishing (or getting other involved parties to publish) any significant information about the world you can somewhere, so that third-parties can work with more substantial information for a better page (with proper citations too!) [[User:Usr edc96730-b899-466c-b373-34e59e839444|Usr edc96730-b899-466c-b373-34e59e839444]] ([[User talk:Usr edc96730-b899-466c-b373-34e59e839444|talk]]) 03:24, 5 October 2024 (UTC)